## Backup strategy

- Automated database backups (daily + continuous if available)
- Store backups in a separate region/account when possible
- Encrypt backups at rest
- Test restore quarterly

```bash
my backup run --dry-run
my backup run
```

## Failover outline

1. Declare incident severity
2. Promote replica / restore latest good backup
3. Point DNS / load balancer to healthy environment
4. Validate critical user journeys
5. Communicate recovery complete

